O'FALLON CHAMBER OF COMMERCE: Mike Morrill Celebrates 43 years in Business!

Business

By Press release submission | Jan 15, 2019


AddThis Sharing Sidebar
Share to Facebook
, Number of shares
Share to TwitterShare to Reddit
, Number of shares
More AddThis Share options
, Number of shares
Hide
Show

O'Fallon Chamber of Commerce issued the following announcement on Jan. 9.

The O’Fallon-Shiloh Chamber of Commerce joined State Farm – Mike Morrill as he celebrated 43 years in business and the opening of his new location at 102 Ruth Drive in O’Fallon. They celebrated with a ribbon cutting ceremony on December 18th.

Mike Morrill and his team are committed to helping State Farm clients manage the unexpected and realize their dreams by protecting the assets they have worked hard to build. Mike has been an engaged member and small business owner in the O’Fallon community for over 43 years. His vast knowledge and experience comprised throughout his team allow his office to help with auto, home, life, health, and small business needs. The unique dual agency privilege also allows this office to service and protect residents in both Illinois and Missouri.

This office’s valuable experience drives Mike Morrill’s State Farm to gainfully compete with other companies and position you best with your insurance needs. Please join us in celebrating 43 successful years in the O’Fallon community at our new office location, 102 Ruth Dr. O’Fallon, Illinois. If you are not a State Farm client; please come by and let us earn your business with a free customized quote.

Visit us at our website: www.MikeMorrillInsurance.com.

THANK YOU, O’Fallon for 43 Successful Years!

Original source can be found here.

Source: O'Fallon Chamber of Commerce
